We have used web2py framework for developing this app.
Which is hosted in Pythonanywhere, please click on the link given below.
http://praful.pythonanywhere.com/

Features:-
Login(Enter email id and password)
Register (Verification link to complete the signup process)
Forgot Password (Verification link to update password)
Profile: at any time user can update his profile.

Enter the place name or select from the suggested list it will display it's temperature and weather condition.
Please wait for few seconds as it may take few seconds to load.


Credits:- www.accuweather.com for providing weather api.